    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/cdb823e498dd8d46921d661179270105.poster.avif?t=1756985899\" width=550 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/cdb823e498dd8d46921d661179270105.webm?t=1756985899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/cdb823e498dd8d46921d661179270105.mp4?t=1756985899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soul Stalker是一款子弹地狱类的roguelike游戏，你将扮演一个受困于尘世的幽灵看守者。你需要同时使用4到6种武器，抵御一波又一波想要打败你幽灵朋友的幻象。从21个角色、35种武器、84件小饰品和21个宠物中选择，打造你的终极装备！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/462bb4f1275b97cd8e37dd6288065e81.poster.avif?t=1756985899\" width=550 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/462bb4f1275b97cd8e37dd6288065e81.webm?t=1756985899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/462bb4f1275b97cd8e37dd6288065e81.mp4?t=1756985899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速且独特的冒险</strong>：在Soul Stalker中，每次游戏都会带你到不同的地点，确保每次约25分钟的游戏体验都独一无二！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>元进程</strong>：通过完成外部世界的任务，购买初始装备，并与Soul Stalkers协会中心的幽灵对话来提升力量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>纸质世界</strong>：沉浸在视觉上引人注目的纸质艺术风格中，呈现2D角色在3D卡通渲染的世界里。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存</strong>：每波持续30到60秒。生存下来并尽可能多地收集资源，在商店和营火处升级你的角色！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/7695bd1d1862ba9e00a33c82d35f41f3.poster.avif?t=1756985899\" width=550 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/7695bd1d1862ba9e00a33c82d35f41f3.webm?t=1756985899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714240/extras/7695bd1d1862ba9e00a33c82d35f41f3.mp4?t=1756985899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
